sequenceDiagram
    participant W as Workers (N permits)
    participant API as Inference Endpoint
    Note over W,API: Healthy - permits cycle fast, high throughput
    API-->>W: 429 (overloaded)
    W->>W: back-off + jitter (permit held during sleep)
    Note over W: fewer permits free - fewer new calls start
    Note over API: incoming request rate DROPS automatically
    API-->>W: recovers (200 OK)
    Note over W,API: permits cycle fast again - throughput ramps back up
